@startuml episode
autonumber
actor "Joueur" as P
participant ":Système" as S
actor "MJ" as M

P -> S: ajouteEpisodeBrouillon(idPersonnage, contenu)
S --> P: confirmeSauvegardeBrouillon(idEpisode)
note right of P: Le joueur rédige et sauvegarde\nun brouillon.

... Plus tard ...

P -> S: demandeValidationEpisode(idEpisode)
S --> P: confirmeDemandeEnvoyée()
S -> M: notifieDemandeValidation(idEpisode, idPersonnage)

... Plus tard ...

M -> S: consulteEpisodeEnAttente(idEpisode)
S --> M: afficheEpisode(contenu, paragraphesSecrets)
M -> S: accepteValidationEpisode(idEpisode)
S -> S: metAJourStatutEpisode("Définitif")
S --> M: confirmeValidation()
S -> P: notifieEpisodeValidé(idEpisode)
@enduml